| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1513 — Recovery Inhibition (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 483391b0-d364-58d2-a941-83d0d8a2d4f5"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
